      ```javascript
      const context = {
        script,
        params,

          WebBrowser,
          Platform,
          Alert,
          NativeAsyncStorage,
          Location,
          Permissions,
          Device,
          Api,
          Sound,
          Notifications,
          TaskManager,
          React,
          wx: this
        }
      }
      ```

      ```javascript
      // 返回 Promise

        resolve(1 + 1)
      })
      ```
